{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Mat|25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","chapter":25,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":1,"text":"“At that time the kingdom of heaven will be like ten virgins who took their lamps and went out to meet the groom.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":2,"text":"Five of them were foolish and five were wise.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":3,"text":"When the foolish took their lamps, they didn’t take oil with them;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":4,"text":"but the wise ones took oil in their flasks with their lamps.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":5,"text":"When the groom was delayed, they all became drowsy and fell asleep.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":6,"text":"“In the middle of the night there was a shout: ‘Here’s the groom! Come out to meet him.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":7,"text":"“Then all the virgins got up and trimmed their lamps.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":8,"text":"The foolish ones said to the wise ones, ‘Give us some of your oil, because our lamps are going out.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":9,"text":"“The wise ones answered, ‘No, there won’t be enough for us and for you. Go instead to those who sell oil, and buy some for yourselves.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":10,"text":"“When they had gone to buy some, the groom arrived, and those who were ready went in with him to the wedding banquet, and the door was shut.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":11,"text":"Later the rest of the virgins also came and said, ‘Master, master, open up for us!’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":12,"text":"“He replied, ‘Truly I tell you, I don’t know you!’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":13,"text":"“Therefore be alert, because you don’t know either the day or the hour.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":14,"text":"“For it is just like a man about to go on a journey. He called his own servants and entrusted his possessions to them.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":15,"text":"To one he gave five talents, to another two talents, and to another one talent, depending on each one’s ability. Then he went on a journey. Immediately","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":16,"text":"the man who had received five talents went, put them to work, and earned five more.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":17,"text":"In the same way the man with two earned two more.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":18,"text":"But the man who had received one talent went off, dug a hole in the ground, and hid his master’s money.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":19,"text":"“After a long time the master of those servants came and settled accounts with them.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":20,"text":"The man who had received five talents approached, presented five more talents, and said, ‘Master, you gave me five talents. See, I’ve earned five more talents.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":21,"text":"“His master said to him, ‘Well done, good and faithful servant! You were faithful over a few things; I will put you in charge of many things. Share your master’s joy.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":22,"text":"“The man with two talents also approached. He said, ‘Master, you gave me two talents. See, I’ve earned two more talents.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":23,"text":"“His master said to him, ‘Well done, good and faithful servant! You were faithful over a few things; I will put you in charge of many things. Share your master’s joy.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":24,"text":"“The man who had received one talent also approached and said, ‘Master, I know you. You’re a harsh man, reaping where you haven’t sown and gathering where you haven’t scattered seed.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":25,"text":"So I was afraid and went off and hid your talent in the ground. See, you have what is yours.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":26,"text":"“His master replied to him, ‘You evil, lazy servant! If you knew that I reap where I haven’t sown and gather where I haven’t scattered,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":27,"text":"then you should have deposited my money with the bankers, and I would have received my money back with interest when I returned.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":28,"text":"“ ‘So take the talent from him and give it to the one who has ten talents.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":29,"text":"For to everyone who has, more will be given, and he will have more than enough. But from the one who does not have, even what he has will be taken away from him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:30","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":30,"text":"And throw this good-for-nothing servant into the outer darkness, where there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:31","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":31,"text":"“When the Son of Man comes in his glory, and all the angels with him, then he will sit on his glorious throne.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:32","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":32,"text":"All the nations will be gathered before him, and he will separate them one from another, just as a shepherd separates the sheep from the goats.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:33","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":33,"text":"He will put the sheep on his right and the goats on the left.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:34","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":34,"text":"Then the King will say to those on his right, ‘Come, you who are blessed by my Father; inherit the kingdom prepared for you from the foundation of the world.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:35","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":35,"text":"“ ‘For I was hungry and you gave me something to eat; I was thirsty and you gave me something to drink; I was a stranger and you took me in;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:36","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":36,"text":"I was naked and you clothed me; I was sick and you took care of me; I was in prison and you visited me.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:37","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":37,"text":"“Then the righteous will answer him, ‘Lord, when did we see you hungry and feed you, or thirsty and give you something to drink?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:38","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":38,"text":"When did we see you a stranger and take you in, or without clothes and clothe you?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:39","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":39,"text":"When did we see you sick, or in prison, and visit you?’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:40","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":40,"text":"“And the King will answer them, ‘Truly I tell you, whatever you did for one of the least of these brothers and sisters of mine, you did for me.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:41","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":41,"text":"“Then he will also say to those on the left, ‘Depart from me, you who are cursed, into the eternal fire prepared for the devil and his angels!","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:42","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":42,"text":"For I was hungry and you gave me nothing to eat; I was thirsty and you gave me nothing to drink;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:43","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":43,"text":"I was a stranger and you didn’t take me in; I was naked and you didn’t clothe me, sick and in prison and you didn’t take care of me.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:44","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":44,"text":"“Then they too will answer, ‘Lord, when did we see you hungry, or thirsty, or a stranger, or without clothes, or sick, or in prison, and not help you?’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:45","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":45,"text":"“Then he will answer them, ‘Truly I tell you, whatever you did not do for one of the least of these, you did not do for me.’","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:46","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","bookOrder":39,"chapter":25,"verse":46,"text":"“And they will go away into eternal punishment, but the righteous into eternal life.”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Mat","chapter":25,"paragraphStarts":[1,6,7,9,10,12,13,14,19,21,22,23,24,26,28,31,35,37,40,41,44,45,46],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"The Parable of the Ten Virgins"},{"beforeVerse":14,"text":"The Parable of the Talents"},{"beforeVerse":31,"text":"The Sheep and the Goats"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“At that time the kingdom of heaven will be like ten virgins"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or bridesmaids"},{"kind":"text","text":" who took their lamps"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or torches, also in vv. 3,4,7,8"},{"kind":"text","text":" and went out to meet the groom."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:24","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 20:8","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 4:5","book":"Rev","chapter":4,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 19:7","book":"Rev","chapter":19,"verse":7,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 21:2","book":"Rev","chapter":21,"verse":2,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 21:9","book":"Rev","chapter":21,"verse":9,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 13:24","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":24},{"label":"Ac 20:8","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":8},{"label":"Rv 4:5","book":"Rev","chapter":4,"verse":5},{"label":"Rv 19:7","book":"Rev","chapter":19,"verse":7},{"label":"Rv 21:2","book":"Rev","chapter":21,"verse":2},{"label":"Rv 21:9","book":"Rev","chapter":21,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or bridesmaids"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or torches, also in vv. 3,4,7,8"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Five of them were foolish and five were wise."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:24","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:16","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:45","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":45,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 7:24","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":24},{"label":"Mt 10:16","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":16},{"label":"Mt 24:45","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":45}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When the foolish took their lamps, they didn’t take oil with them; "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"but the wise ones took oil in their flasks with their lamps. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When the groom was delayed, they all became drowsy and fell asleep."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“In the middle of the night there was a shout: ‘Here’s the groom! Come out to meet him.’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Then all the virgins got up and trimmed their lamps. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The foolish ones said to the wise ones, ‘Give us some of your oil, because our lamps are going out.’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“The wise ones answered, ‘No, there won’t be enough for us and for you. Go instead to those who sell oil, and buy some for yourselves.’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“When they had gone to buy some, the groom arrived, and those who were ready went in with him to the wedding banquet, and the door was shut."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 22:2","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 13:25","book":"Luk","chapter":13,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 22:2","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":2},{"label":"Lk 13:25","book":"Luk","chapter":13,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Later the rest of the virgins also came and said, ‘Master, master, open up for us!’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“He replied, ‘Truly I tell you, I don’t know you!’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Therefore be alert, because you don’t know either the day or the hour."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add in which the Son of Man is coming."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add in which the Son of Man is coming."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“For it is just like a man about to go on a journey."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 19:12–27","book":"Luk","chapter":19,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" He called his own servants and entrusted his possessions to them. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 19:12–27","book":"Luk","chapter":19,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"To one he gave five talents,"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"A talent is worth about 6,000 denarii, or twenty years’ wages for a laborer"},{"kind":"text","text":" to another two talents, and to another one talent, depending on each one’s ability. Then he went on a journey."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:24","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 19:13","book":"Luk","chapter":19,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 12:6","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 12:11","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":11,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:7","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" Immediately "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 18:24","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":24},{"label":"Lk 19:13","book":"Luk","chapter":19,"verse":13},{"label":"Rm 12:6","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":6},{"label":"1Co 12:11","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":11},{"label":"Eph 4:7","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"A talent is worth about 6,000 denarii, or twenty years’ wages for a laborer"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"the man who had received five talents went, put them to work, and earned five more. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In the same way the man with two earned two more. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the man who had received one talent went off, dug a hole in the ground, and hid his master’s money."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“After a long time the master of those servants came and settled accounts with them. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The man who had received five talents approached, presented five more talents, and said, ‘Master, you gave me five talents. See, I’ve earned five more talents.’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“His master said to him, ‘Well done, good and faithful servant! You were faithful over a few things; I will put you in charge of many things. Share your master’s joy.’"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:45","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":45,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:47","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":47,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:44","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":44,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 22:28","book":"Luk","chapter":22,"verse":28,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 12:2","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":2,"letter":"e"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 24:45","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":45},{"label":"Mt 24:47","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":47},{"label":"Lk 12:44","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":44},{"label":"Lk 22:28","book":"Luk","chapter":22,"verse":28},{"label":"Heb 12:2","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“The man with two talents also approached. He said, ‘Master, you gave me two talents. See, I’ve earned two more talents.’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“His master said to him, ‘Well done, good and faithful servant! You were faithful over a few things; I will put you in charge of many things. Share your master’s joy.’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“The man who had received one talent also approached and said, ‘Master, I know you. You’re a harsh man, reaping where you haven’t sown and gathering where you haven’t scattered seed."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 25:3","book":"1Sa","chapter":25,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 8:12","book":"2Co","chapter":8,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 25:3","book":"1Sa","chapter":25,"verse":3},{"label":"2Co 8:12","book":"2Co","chapter":8,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So I was afraid and went off and hid your talent in the ground. See, you have what is yours.’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“His master replied to him, ‘You evil, lazy servant!"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 20:4","book":"Pro","chapter":20,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:32","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":32,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 12:11","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" If you knew that I reap where I haven’t sown and gather where I haven’t scattered, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 20:4","book":"Pro","chapter":20,"verse":4},{"label":"Mt 18:32","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":32},{"label":"Rm 12:11","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"then"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or So you knew... scattered? Then (as a question)"},{"kind":"text","text":" you should have deposited my money with the bankers, and I would have received my money"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit received what is mine"},{"kind":"text","text":" back with interest when I returned."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or So you knew... scattered? Then (as a question)"},{"marker":2,"text":"Lit received what is mine"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“ ‘So take the talent from him and give it to the one who has ten talents. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For to everyone who has, more will be given, and he will have more than enough. But from the one who does not have, even what he has will be taken away from him."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:12","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 4:25","book":"Mrk","chapter":4,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 8:18","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 19:26","book":"Luk","chapter":19,"verse":26,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 15:2","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":2,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 13:12","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":12},{"label":"Mk 4:25","book":"Mrk","chapter":4,"verse":25},{"label":"Lk 8:18","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":18},{"label":"Lk 19:26","book":"Luk","chapter":19,"verse":26},{"label":"Jn 15:2","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And throw this good-for-nothing servant into the outer darkness,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:12","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 22:13","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 13:28","book":"Luk","chapter":13,"verse":28,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" where there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.’"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 8:12","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":12},{"label":"Mt 22:13","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":13},{"label":"Lk 13:28","book":"Luk","chapter":13,"verse":28}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“When the Son of Man comes in his glory, and all the angels"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read holy angels"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 16:7","book":"Gen","chapter":16,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:34","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":34,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:49","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":49,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:11","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:19","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":19,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 14:6","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":6,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" with him, then he will sit on his glorious throne."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:27","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":27,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 19:28","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":28,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 1:7","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:14","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:7","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 16:7","book":"Gen","chapter":16,"verse":7},{"label":"Mt 5:34","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":34},{"label":"Mt 13:49","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":49},{"label":"Lk 1:11","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 5:19","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":19},{"label":"Rv 14:6","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":6},{"label":"Mt 16:27","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":27},{"label":"Mt 19:28","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":28},{"label":"2Th 1:7","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"Jd 1:14","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":14},{"label":"Rv 1:7","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read holy angels"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"All the nations"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or the Gentiles"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jl 3:12","book":"Jol","chapter":3,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:14","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 28:19","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":19,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:5","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:16","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" will be gathered before him, and he will separate them one from another, just as a shepherd separates the sheep from the goats."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:17","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":17,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 34:20","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":20,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:49","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":49,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jl 3:12","book":"Jol","chapter":3,"verse":12},{"label":"Mt 24:14","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":14},{"label":"Mt 28:19","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":19},{"label":"Rm 1:5","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"Gl 1:16","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"Ezk 34:17","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":17},{"label":"Ezk 34:20","book":"Ezk","chapter":34,"verse":20},{"label":"Mt 13:49","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":49}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or the Gentiles"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He will put the sheep on his right and the goats on the left. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then the King will say to those on his right, ‘Come, you who are blessed by my Father; inherit the kingdom"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 19:29","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:32","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":32,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:50","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":50,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:21","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":21,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:5","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:9","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 21:7","book":"Rev","chapter":21,"verse":7,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" prepared for you from the foundation of the world."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:35","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":35,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 20:23","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":23,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 2:9","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 4:3","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":3,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:26","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":26,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:16","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":16,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 13:8","book":"Rev","chapter":13,"verse":8,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 17:8","book":"Rev","chapter":17,"verse":8,"letter":"o"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 19:29","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":29},{"label":"Lk 12:32","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":32},{"label":"1Co 15:50","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":50},{"label":"Gl 5:21","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":21},{"label":"Jms 2:5","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":5},{"label":"1Pt 3:9","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":9},{"label":"Rv 21:7","book":"Rev","chapter":21,"verse":7},{"label":"Mt 13:35","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":35},{"label":"Mt 20:23","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":23},{"label":"1Co 2:9","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":9},{"label":"Heb 4:3","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":3},{"label":"Heb 9:26","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":26},{"label":"Heb 11:16","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":16},{"label":"Rv 13:8","book":"Rev","chapter":13,"verse":8},{"label":"Rv 17:8","book":"Rev","chapter":17,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:35","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“ ‘For I was hungry and you gave me something to eat; I was thirsty and you gave me something to drink; I was a stranger and you took me in; "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:36","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I was naked and you clothed me; I was sick and you took care of me; I was in prison and you visited me.’"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 31:32","book":"Job","chapter":31,"verse":32,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 58:7","book":"Isa","chapter":58,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 18:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":18,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:16","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 13:2","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":2,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 1:27","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":27,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:15–16","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":15,"letter":"g"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 31:32","book":"Job","chapter":31,"verse":32},{"label":"Is 58:7","book":"Isa","chapter":58,"verse":7},{"label":"Ezk 18:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":18,"verse":7},{"label":"2Tm 1:16","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"Heb 13:2","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":2},{"label":"Jms 1:27","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":27},{"label":"Jms 2:15–16","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:37","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Then the righteous will answer him, ‘Lord, when did we see you hungry and feed you, or thirsty and give you something to drink? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:38","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When did we see you a stranger and take you in, or without clothes and clothe you? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:39","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When did we see you sick, or in prison, and visit you?’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:40","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“And the King will answer them, ‘Truly I tell you, whatever you did for one of the least of these brothers and sisters of mine, you did for me.’"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 19:17","book":"Pro","chapter":19,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:42","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":42,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 25:34","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":34,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 6:10","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":10,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 19:17","book":"Pro","chapter":19,"verse":17},{"label":"Mt 10:42","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":42},{"label":"Mt 25:34","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":34},{"label":"Heb 6:10","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:41","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Then he will also say to those on the left, ‘Depart from me, you who are cursed, into the eternal fire prepared for the devil and his angels!"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:23","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:40","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":40,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:42","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":42,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 9:48","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":48,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:4","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:6","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 7:23","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":23},{"label":"Mt 13:40","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":40},{"label":"Mt 13:42","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":42},{"label":"Mk 9:48","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":48},{"label":"2Pt 2:4","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Jd 1:6","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:42","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I was hungry and you gave me nothing to eat; I was thirsty and you gave me nothing to drink; "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:43","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I was a stranger and you didn’t take me in; I was naked and you didn’t clothe me, sick and in prison and you didn’t take care of me.’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:44","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Then they too will answer, ‘Lord, when did we see you hungry, or thirsty, or a stranger, or without clothes, or sick, or in prison, and not help you?’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:45","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Then he will answer them, ‘Truly I tell you, whatever you did not do for one of the least of these, you did not do for me.’"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 14:31","book":"Pro","chapter":14,"verse":31,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 17:5","book":"Pro","chapter":17,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:5","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":5,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 14:31","book":"Pro","chapter":14,"verse":31},{"label":"Pr 17:5","book":"Pro","chapter":17,"verse":5},{"label":"Ac 9:5","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:25:46","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“And they will go away into eternal punishment, but the righteous into eternal life.”"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 12:2","book":"Dan","chapter":12,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 5:21","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":21,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 24:15","book":"Act","chapter":24,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 2:7","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":7,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dn 12:2","book":"Dan","chapter":12,"verse":2},{"label":"Jn 5:21","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":21},{"label":"Ac 24:15","book":"Act","chapter":24,"verse":15},{"label":"Rm 2:7","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099502007}